  "Account address of the sender"

  "Account address of the receiver"
  receiver: Account!

  positions: [Position!]!
  "Market associated with the transfer"
  market: Market!

  amount: BigInt!
  "Value of the transferred amount in USD"
  amountUSD: BigDecimal!
}"}
